Philippe Duquesne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philippe_Duquesne 0 Philippe Duquesne (born 30 June 1965) is a French actor. He is best known for playing in the cult TV series Les Deschiens (1993–2002), in which he plays alongside Yolande Moreau. Philippe_Duquesne ( born_30_June_1965 ) is a_French_actor .
